{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_017n4PHR9dZLSr9KwxHJKN9J","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus to Jakarta EE\n\n### What was done\nThe Coffee Shop application was migrated from **Quarkus 3.30.5** to **Jakarta EE 10 on Open Liberty**.\n\n### Key technology replacements\n| Quarkus | Jakarta EE |\n|---------|-----------|\n| Panache ORM | Standard JPA with EntityManager |\n| Vert.x EventBus | CDI Events (`@Observes`) |\n| SmallRye Reactive Messaging (Kafka) | CDI Events (in-memory) |\n| Qute templates | Inline HTML |\n| Mutiny SSE | Jakarta REST SSE (`SseBroadcaster`) |\n| Quarkus Dev Services (PostgreSQL) | H2 in-memory database |\n| Hibernate | EclipseLink |\n\n### Issues resolved\n1. **Test compilation**: Fixed static vs instance method call on `Order.apply()`\n2. **H2 URL format**: Fixed Liberty datasource `properties` element\n3. **EclipseLink DDL**: Changed `GenerationType.IDENTITY` to `AUTO` for H2\n4. **Instant type mapping**: Created `InstantAttributeConverter` to bridge EclipseLink's lack of native `java.time.Instant` support\n5. **HTTP header errors**: Added `GlobalExceptionMapper` to sanitize multi-line error messages\n6. **Idempotent tests**: Added timestamp-based unique order IDs to smoke tests\n\n### Results\n- **Build**: SUCCESS\n- **Docker image**: Built and runs on Open Liberty\n- **Smoke tests**: **8/8 passed, 0 failed**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":125,"cache_read_input_tokens":78943,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":125,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":406},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"55a9df99-a1b9-45b0-ac12-d337ab838722","uuid":"b7e24f97-8f3a-47ba-a49b-d05840171639"}
